data.description: ATTENTION INVESTORS !! HOUSE IS RENTED UNTIL 4/30/2024. . . . This property comes with the added advantage of a responsible and reliable tenant who is committed to maintaining the home.  This provides you with immediate rental income and peace of mind that the property is well cared for. The lease expires in March 2024, and the tenants are interested in continuing leasing if the new owner is in agreement.  Two-story with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths.  All bedrooms upstairs. The spacious living room is bathed in natural light and Neutral tones.   Conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and major transportation routes, this home offers easy access to everything you need.  The neighborhood's friendly atmosphere makes it a great property!!
